YOU'RE HOLDING BACK.

23:42.980 --> 23:44.516
YOU AND ME, WE GOT
TO STOP WORRYING

23:44.520 --> 23:46.682
ABOUT THE PARENTS
WHO REJECTED US, MAN.

23:46.690 --> 23:49.910
THIS ABOUT YOUR DAD
BEING HERE?

23:49.920 --> 23:51.922
YEAH. HA HA.

23:51.930 --> 23:54.900
RIGHT? YOU AIN'T THE ONLY ONE
THAT KNOWS SOME THINGS, OK?

23:54.900 --> 23:57.551
HA HA.

23:57.560 --> 24:00.097
YOU KNOW I GOT TICKETS?

24:00.100 --> 24:01.192
YOU GONNA GO?

24:01.200 --> 24:03.396
NAH.

24:03.400 --> 24:05.562
I MEAN, I THOUGHT
ABOUT IT, BUT...

24:05.570 --> 24:07.060
BECAUSE YOU GOT TO
ROLL WITH THE PEOPLE

24:07.070 --> 24:09.209
WHO ALWAYS BEEN
THERE FOR YOU, RIGHT,

24:09.210 --> 24:11.406
WHO ALWAYS ACCEPT
YOU FOR YOU?

24:21.420 --> 24:23.855
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

24:28.430 --> 24:31.070
MY GRANDKIDS INVITED ME.

24:35.100 --> 24:36.738
YOU INVITED HIM HERE?

24:36.740 --> 24:38.560
HOW IS IT THAT YOU'RE MAD
AT US RIGHT NOW?

24:38.570 --> 24:40.902
YOU'RE THE ONE THAT LIED ABOUT
OUR GRANDFATHER OUR WHOLE LIVES.

24:40.910 --> 24:42.400
-LOOK, IT'S COMPLICATED.

24:42.410 --> 24:43.673
HE LIVES HALF AN HOUR AWAY.

24:43.680 --> 24:45.444
WHY WOULD YOU
HIDE HIM FROM US?

24:45.450 --> 24:48.044
BILLY: LOOK, OK. I REALIZE
THIS IS CONFUSING FOR YOU BOTH.

24:48.050 --> 24:51.486
I HAD TO MAKE A DECISION
FOR THIS FAMILY, OK,

24:51.490 --> 24:52.980
AND IT WAS THE RIGHT
DECISION.

24:52.990 --> 24:55.914
OLIVIA: SAYS WHO?
BILLY: SAYS ME, THAT'S WHO.

24:55.920 --> 24:57.558
I'M GONNA TELL HIM, HE'S
GOT TO GET OUT OF HERE.

24:57.560 --> 24:59.050
OLIVIA: WHAT? NO, WHY
DOES HE HAVE TO LEAVE?

24:59.060 --> 25:01.256
JORDAN: YOU AFRAID
SOMETHING WILL COME OUT, DAD?

25:01.260 --> 25:02.853
WHAT IS THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

25:02.860 --> 25:05.466
DO YOU THINK I'M KEEPING
SECRETS FROM YOU?

25:05.470 --> 25:06.926
